{"tid":777851,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我地會feel到比人注視緊？","createTime":"2018-08-13T09:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T04:22:35.000Z","uid":138728,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bca5d4d6f2982e2471566d29a877f778d85249","tid":777851,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:01:59.000Z","msg":"話說我做功課玩電腦個陣成日比呀婆偷望<br />\n我望番佢話：你做咩望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀婆就會駁我：你夠望我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔望我又點知我望你<br />\n我同佢講呢個係動物既天性<br />\n佢又話我痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上左google 搵發現其實而家都未用科學解釋得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剩係有啲實驗證明左我地確實係我呢種能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲學者推論可能係關眼球曈孔同 虹膜事<br />\n又有人話帶黑超又有影響<br />\n<br />\n我覺得隔住其他野望人都有影響<br />\n因為係巴士昅女唔會比人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係又解釋唔到我平時帶左眼鏡望又會比人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fff1d634691a372e345a5f1f0349148d7f9cc5","tid":777851,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91b0a733ef9c94ac8e8a0383cebc5b832c9f8209","tid":777851,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"你計埋屎眼就明"},{"pid":"776d969e44580233f509e6dea3aac5a8afcbaeb9","tid":777851,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"402b22de9b1177276609a5f60c3a191c2a8f09b9","tid":777851,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"其實係心理作用"},{"pid":"8da5f60129e1473a263a56134f7c63f558ebba13","tid